CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: CIMG Inc. is a digital health and sales company, which focuses on digital marketing, sales, and distribution of various consumer goods related to food and beverages. Dedicated to reshaping the digital marketing and distribution with technological applications, the Company endeavors to create greater commercial value for its business partners and enhance its enterprise and shareholders' value.The Company has a professional brand and marketing management system, which can quickly help partnering enterprises achieve the connection, management, and operation of marketing channels domestically and globally.The Company's products include maca peptide coffee, Maca Noni beverages, maca purified powder, and qianmao wine.
